{"tid":2142700,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"博士生稱6.12受催淚煙襲擊入稟告警務處  律政司以「瑣碎無聊或無理纏擾」要求審裁處剔除申索","createTime":"2020-08-06T14:49:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-06T17:27:58.000Z","uid":22556,"like":7,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"1746aff17ff5e3381e4e73487480789d48f2e0e7","tid":2142700,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T14:49:53.000Z","msg":"科大博士生去年入稟小額錢債審裁處，就6.12吸入催淚煙而受到精神困擾，以及警方無理驅散和平集會，而向警方索償。代表警方的律政司以相關申索屬<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">「瑣碎無聊或無理纏擾」為由，要求審裁處剔除申索</span></span></strong>，惟今年5月遭審裁官駁回。案件原本應進入正式訴訟，但律政司近日再向高等法院提出上訴，要求剔除相關申索。案件今日（6日）在小額錢債審裁處聆訊，審裁官認為需等待高院上訴結果後才能繼續申索程序，故押後案件至11月6日再訊。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">律政司不服審裁官今年5月批准案件正式訴訟，近日入稟高等法院提出上訴，並已獲得上訴許可，但暫未排期作上訴聆訊。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1076193\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1076193&d=il%2BrReVPph3FBkDtfLAFOm6H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=4582b4a3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1076193&h=593a0227\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1076193</a>"},{"pid":"e5179304da5e3586123b47f8783a15a95b6d5d3a","tid":2142700,"uid":9193,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T14:54:38.000Z","msg":"黑警成日亂告<br />\n算唔算瑣碎無聊或無理纏擾？"},{"pid":"b80f2a58ea534ba88997de5de87a1d5f0b5b45b4","tid":2142700,"uid":132587,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T14:56:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"10ebc6008cefe541130c876cccd2ec8a5eaaffff","tid":2142700,"uid":9193,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"b80f2a58ea534ba88997de5de87a1d5f0b5b45b4","tid":2142700,"uid":132587,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"quote":{"pid":"e5179304da5e3586123b47f8783a15a95b6d5d3a","tid":2142700,"uid":9193,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T14:54:38.000Z","msg":"黑警成日亂